<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="494" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1436,419,591]" pageId="5" pageNumber="494">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,274,419,446]" pageId="5" pageNumber="494">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Tegmen black with extensive elongated orangish-red markings. Subgenital plate with dorsal margin with rounded elevation, covered with small tooth-like spines. Paramere robust with spine-like dorsal subapical anteroventrally directed process, and more basal ventral posteriorly directed, straight, spine-like process.
</paragraph>
